section.div: A simple license plates recognition web platform

Vibe_Coding_Workflow is an engineering-grade workflow for using AI in long-running software projects. It turns AI from a context-dependent chat tool into a file-driven collaborator, addressing context loss, implicit assumptions, decision drift, and AIhuman inconsistency.
